{"tid":1346093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721元朗影片整理","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:17:18.000Z","uid":44916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c6c6f84aa17350c8a725c013bd16fd257b9751","tid":1346093,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:29:51.000Z","msg":"可能已經有人做緊，無就當開個頭，<br />\n因為過咗一晚啲片喺個Facebook Wall上面有啲亂，<br />\n想集中返啲Facebook, Youtube等等影片，幫下文宣、搜證、搵老豆、方便Share畀人<br />\n請大家喺呢個Post貼返晒尋晚啲片，最好提供簡短描述方便我分辨同整理<br />\n<br />\n已整理嘅會集中更新到以下呢條連結方便大家睇返，<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.evernote.com/shard/s323/sh/612c398c-6c0a-4d1d-9ac8-d849e3aa560b/572aca9b3e6ffe9c1e7a4b91b97d8a0a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.evernote.com%2Fshard%2Fs323%2Fsh%2F612c398c-6c0a-4d1d-9ac8-d849e3aa560b%2F572aca9b3e6ffe9c1e7a4b91b97d8a0a&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=f4755bff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.evernote.com/shard/s323/sh/612c398c-6c0a-4d1d-9ac8-d849e3aa560b/572aca9b3e6ffe9c1e7a4b91b97d8a0a</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時會加返啲中文描述，如果用字有咩唔啱請回覆提點，同講返有冇影到施襲者嘅樣<br />\n後續可能加返晒英文描述，方便外媒<br />\n<br />\n如果真係無Account就Email去hongkong201907@gmail.com"},{"pid":"db1ce6b54f93087527c56e7b6b48cea52755a08a","tid":1346093,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c46f856527ad8e7e7a1c08585e7babdc521363","tid":1346093,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461690093807b9747c7cd8b01e3e8ac559ed21ec","tid":1346093,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153cbe999c684f217ae3bba1dd5ce045857d4654","tid":1346093,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"